                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1431541/">要振作的牡蛎君</a>
                    <span>2015-09-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">购于上海书展，有幸听作者本人和刘绪源老师讲书，得签名赠言。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
